column5: Hey, this worked pretty well last year for my group’s fly-in, so I think I’ll try it again! Has anyone here fished McInnes Lake before? We’re considering it. It’s a huge lake, very long and deep, with three cabins on it, and a small portage or two. Lake trout, northern, and walleye inhabit the lake. Just wondering if anyone’s experienced this lake or Viking Outposts in general before, any information I could get would be appreciated. Thanks guys!
